dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents tax parcels for Sauk County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Sauk_Parcels_2016.gdb. Additional features included in this geodatabase are zoning information: 'AIRPORT', 'FARMLAND', 'FLOODPLAIN', 'GENERAL', and 'SHORELAND'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://data-saukgis.opendata.arcgis.com/
